<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/family-procedure-rule-committee> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Family Procedure Rule Committee (FPRC) makes rules of court that govern the practice and procedure followed in family proceedings in the High Court and family court. FPRC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ."@en .
